OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FThe lead commissioner of Birmingham
OL,7,FCity Council, who has been overseeing
OL,8,F#300m of cuts to council services over
OL,9,Fthe last two years, is stepping down
OL,10,Ffrom his role.
OL,12,FMax Caller, who has been referred to
OL,13,Fby campaigners across the city as "Max
OL,14,Fthe Axe", has announced plans to
OL,15,Fretire.
OL,17,FHe was sent in by the Government in
OL,18,F2023 to make hundreds of millions of
OL,19,Fpounds worth of cuts to services after
OL,20,Fthe authority effectively declared
OL,21,Fbankruptcy.
OL,26,@uD@cOUvD@HO]
