OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FHe will be replaced by Tony McArdle
OL,7,FOBE, who is the former chief executive
OL,8,Fof Lincolnshire County Council, and
OL,9,FWellingborough Council. He also led
OL,10,Fthe recent intervention at Nottingham
OL,11,FCity Council to help solve their
OL,12,Ffinancial problems two years ago.
OL,14,FIt's understood Mr Caller has written
OL,15,Fto deputy prime minister Angela Rayner
OL,16,Fconfirming his retirement plan.
OL,18,FIt comes in the midst of a hugely
OL,19,Fdamaging bin strike in the city, which
OL,20,Fis understood to have cost the council
OL,21,Fand taxpayers #4 million.
