OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FMr Caller had said last year that he
OL,7,Fintended to step down as soon as he
OL,8,Ffelt the council's recovery and
OL,9,Fimprovement was secure.
OL,11,FHe had said it would be a "disaster"
OL,12,Fif he stayed on for longer as it would
OL,13,Fshow the council was not getting
OL,14,Fbetter.
