OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FIn a statement Jim McMahon, minister
OL,7,Ffor local government and regional
OL,8,Fdevolution at the Ministry of Housing,
OL,9,FLocal Government and Communities has
OL,10,Fsaid: "Max Caller has made a
OL,11,Fsignificant contribution to local
OL,12,Fgovernment throughout his career
OL,13,Fincluding leading efforts to put
OL,14,FBirmingham City Council on a
OL,15,Fsustainable footing.
OL,17,F"We thank him for his work and wish
OL,18,Fhim well in his retirement.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
