OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,F"While the city's recovery remains
OL,7,Ffragile, marked progress was made
OL,8,Funder his leadership including
OL,9,Fdeveloping a stable medium-term
OL,10,Ffinancial plan, making progress
OL,11,Ftowards resolving the outstanding
OL,12,Fequal pay situation, and re-
OL,13,Fimplementing the Oracle IT programme.
OL,15,F"The government's priority is to
OL,16,Fensure this work continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
