OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,F"I am confident that will be the case
OL,7,Funder the new lead commissioner Tony
OL,8,FMcArdle OBE who brings a huge range of
OL,9,Fexperience to the role having been a
OL,10,Fwell-respected council chief executive
OL,11,Fand leading interventions at other
OL,12,Flocal authorities."
OL,14,FHis departure comes just one day after
OL,15,Fcampaigners lost their legal battle
OL,16,Fover his decision to shut four day
OL,17,Fcentres in the city for people with
OL,18,Fdisabilities: Beeches GOLDD, Fairway,
OL,19,FHarborne, and Heartlands.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
