OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FWishing Mr Caller well, the council
OL,7,Fleader, Councillor John Cotton, said:
OL,8,F"I want to place on record our best
OL,9,Fwishes to Max for his retirement and I
OL,10,Fhave thanked him for his valuable
OL,11,Fcontribution in helping Birmingham's
OL,12,Fimprovement over the past two years.
OL,14,F"I have this morning also received a
OL,15,Fletter from the Minister of State for
OL,16,FLocal Government and English
OL,17,FDevolution, Jim McMahon MP. The
OL,18,FMinister has informed us that he has
OL,19,Fappointed Tony McArdle OBE as the new
OL,20,FLead Commissioner at Birmingham City
OL,21,FCouncil.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
