OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F379A1753369122
OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,F"I am clear that the council still
OL,7,Fneeds external support and the
OL,8,Fchallenge of critical friends, but we
OL,9,Fneed to ensure that they are aligned
OL,10,Fto our shared priorities as we move to
OL,11,Fthe next stage of the council's
OL,12,Fimprovement journey.
OL,14,F"We are very keen to continue the pace
OL,15,Fof progress and ensure it does not
OL,16,Fslow down during these changes. That
OL,17,Fis why work on producing next year's
OL,18,Fbudget continues at pace."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
