OL,3,CControversial commissioner who led
OL,4,C#300m of council cuts to step down
OL,6,FSince being appointed by the then
OL,7,FSecretary of State Michael Gove in
OL,8,FOctober 2023, Mr Caller has overseen a
OL,9,Fstring of major cuts to the council's
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FAs commissioner, his role included
OL,13,Fensuring financial sustainability was
OL,14,Fdelivered, closing budget gaps,
OL,15,Fagreeing changes to the authority's
OL,16,Foperating model to ensure financial
OL,17,Fsustainability.
